<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Let the peoples praise you, God;</para>

<para style="q1">let all the peoples praise you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Oh, let the nations be glad and sing for joy,</para>

<para style="q1">for you will judge the peoples with justice</para>

<para style="q1">and govern the nations on earth.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
